
/* This CSS page applies visual styles to the HTML code. The syntax is different to HTML */

/* this is a note
the below section is setting the default font. This requires it to be installed on the device - if not installed, the browser will display in its own default font */
@font-face {
    font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
}


/*
CSS can be applied to elements, ids (use # , be unique in html), or classes (use . , can be applied to many different elements). 
*/



